      "writtenOn": "2018-07-03T17:16:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "before I comment on smaller things in code, how about this high level structure:\n\nh :\u003d impl.loadLogsOfRefs(ctx, refTips)\nheap.Heapify(h)\n// let reader focus on heap based merging.\n\n\n\nwhile loadLogsOfRefs does the heavy lifting related to ds cache:\n\nfromCache, missingSliceOfRefs, err :\u003d loadFromDS(refTips)\nremaining :\u003d // fetch all missing ones from gitiles\nsaveToDS(remaining)\nreturn append(fromCache, remaining...), nil\n\n\nloadFromDS can then fetch all items from DS at once, then filter out \nall those for which either there is no entry, or stale commit hash, or we can\u0027t unmarshall it.\nThis is better than creating N * DS calls from N goroutines.\n\nDitto for saving new cache entries.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 118,
        "startChar": 1,
        "endLine": 122,
        "endChar": 78
      },
      "revId": "bbaaa7e6a5faa9957d2315fd586c32329d4019ee",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
    },
